ENJOY A SLOWER PACE AT RUSH LILY
"The world is changing and you need a home that can adapt to the new-age world."
Do you suddenly find yourself working from home? Are your kids reliant on fast-speed internet? Do you want a private lifestyle but also a home that is great for entertaining?
Then 15 Rush Lily is the perfect lockdown home.
With high-speed NBN available and family-orientated floor plan the property ticks a lot of boxes.
The large study at the front could be used as a fourth bedroom, a salon, a place for an at-home business or ideal location for kids to do homework.
Don't be isolated during isolation.
You're walking distance to parks, ovals and Arena shops. Plus you're within walking distance to a number of top-notch schools.
The house also features:
- Three large bedrooms, master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Large open plan living/dining room;
- Rumpus room;
- Modern kitchen;
- Heating and cooling;
- 9-foot ceilings;
- Alfresco and double car garage;
- Decent backyard (in total approx 400sqm);
- Security alarm.
Book your private appointment today.
