LUCY IN DISGUISE WITH DIAMONDS
"Can't buy me love, but you can buy me 2 Lucy Crescent."
And ain't she sweet. With contemporary flair and style, 2 Lucy Crescent is sure to be a hit. Let it be your next purchase. Only a few minutes walk from Officer Secondary School, Bridgewood Primary and even closer to public transport, your searchin' is finally over the moment you step through the door. Surrounded by the ever-expanding Officer community and still under builders warranty, 2 Lucy Crescent is your ticket to ride.
On a large 508m2 block (approx.), the house features:
- Two enormous living zones;
- Separate dining area;
- Widespread kitchen centrally located with walk-in pantry;
- Three bedrooms, large master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Alfresco with decked entertaining area that sprawls out over the yard and overlooks the well maintained gardens;
- Being a corner block you get the best of a gated side access.
No more crying, waiting, hoping. Spend a day in the life of 2 Lucy Crescent and you'll be here 8 days a week.
